    - Ubuntu maintainers
    - Promote python-lxml, python-numpy, python-uniconvertor to Recommends.
    - Demote pstoedit to Suggests (universe package).
    - Suggests ttf-dejavu instead of ttf-bitstream-vera (LP: #513319)
