  * Acknowledge NMU, which in fact was an upload of my sponsor with my
    knowledge (Closes: #341909, #342194, #342367)
  * Build-Depend on g++ (>= 4:4.0.2-2) on arm/hppa/m68k to get rid of g++-3.4
    on etch
